high_descs: Move forward toward the sink then turn left and move to the counter between the refrigerator and the range.
Pick up the gold knife located between the lettuce and the fork from the counter.
Turn to the left and move toward the refrigerator slightly, then turn to the right and face the counter.
Slice the head of lettuce to the left of the salt shaker on the counter using the knife.
Turn to the right and move toward the range slightly, then turn to the left and face the counter.
Place the knife on top of the fork on the counter between the refrigerator and the range.
Turn to the left and move toward the refrigerator slightly, then turn to the right and face the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sliced head of lettuce on the rear of the counter to the left of the salt shaker.
Turn to the left, move toward the white door, then turn to the right and face the gray refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator doors, place the lettuce on the top shelf to the right of the tomato, allow the lettuce to cool, open the refrigerator, pick up the lettuce from the top shelf and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn right, move towards the range, then turn right, and move to the sink.
Place the slice of lettuce to the right of the drain in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Move forward and face the counter on your left
Grab the large knife that's on the counter
Move slightly to the left
Slice the cabbage that's on the counter with your knife
Move slightly to the right
Place the knife back on the counter
Turn slightly to the left
Grab a piece of the sliced cabbage
Turn to your left and open the fridge
Put the cabbage on the top rack. Close the door, and then take the cabbage out after some time.
Turn to your right and head to the sink
Place the cabbage in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting sliced cabbage in a sink

high_descs: Take a step forward and then turn left and walk forward to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the vegetable on the counter.
Cut the vegetable on the counter into slices.
Step to the right and face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Step to the left and face the vegetable on the counter.
Pick up a slice of the vegetable on the counter.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Cool the slice of vegetable in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the slice of vegetable in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cut a piece of vegetable as well as place it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the counter that's to the left of the oven
Grab the large knife that's on the counter
Move slightly to the left
Slice the cabbage that's on the counter with the knife
Move slightly to the right
Place the knife back on the counter
Move slightly to the left
Grab one of the cabbage slices
Turn to your left and face the fridge
Open the bottom door of the fridge and put the cabbage inside it. Close the door. Open the door, and then take the cabbage out. Then close the door.
Turn around and head to the sink
Place the cabbage in the sink
anns.task_desc: Placing a sliced cabbage in the sink
